devdoc.details: Implementation of the {IKIP13} interface. Contracts that want to implement KIP13 should inherit from this contract and override {supportsInterface} to check for the additional interface id that will be supported. For example: ```solidity function supportsInterface(bytes4 interfaceId) public view virtual override returns (bool) {     return interfaceId == type(MyInterface).interfaceId || super.supportsInterface(interfaceId); } ``` Alternatively, {KIP13Storage} provides an easier to use but more expensive implementation.
